[[Kutapidza]] zvinoreva kutsauranisa [[muchegwa]] ne[[mambara]]. Mambara ndiwo matombo asiri kudiwa asina kukosha; aya matombo anoraswa ku[[motoro]]. Muchegwa ndiwo matombo akatakura simbi; aya matombo anochengetwa achipinda mune dzimwe shandura dzinowedzera [[hutapiri]] hwesimbi. Chinangwa chekutapidza ndechekuti pakupedzisira simbi ive ine [[hutapiri]] hunoramba huchikwira kudzamara yasvika pakunatswa.
